data.description: QUAINT home on corner lot.  2 bedroom, 2 bath, and there's another room that can be a 3rd bedroom.  Nice sized living room. Separate dining room open to the kitchen.  Kitchen bar.  Cute kitchen with dishwasher.  Double paned windows.  Water well in backyard has a pump, but no pressure tank.  Has been used many times to water the .648 acres and had never run dry.  Gigantic yard with two separate fenced areas.  Metal roof with vinyl siding.
